FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our dog walking service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How long are your typical dog walks?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our standard dog walks are 30 minutes long, but we also offer 45-minute and 60-minute options to suit your dog's needs and energy levels.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Do you offer group walks or individual walks?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer both group and individual walks. Group walks are great for socialization, while individual walks provide more focused attention for your dog.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We currently offer dog walking services in [City Name] and surrounding neighborhoods. Please contact us for specific coverage areas.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do I book a walk for my dog?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Booking is easy! You can schedule a walk through our website, mobile app, or by calling our customer service team. We recommend booking at least 24 hours in advance.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What happens if the weather is bad?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We walk dogs in most weather conditions, but in cases of extreme weather (severe storms, extreme heat), we may reschedule the walk or offer an indoor visit for your dog's safety and comfort.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Walking Service
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How long are your typical dog walks?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our standard dog walks are 30 minutes long, but we offer flexible options ranging from 15-minute quick potty breaks to 60-minute extended walks, depending on your dog's needs and your preferences.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Do you offer group walks or individual walks?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We provide both group and individual walks. Group walks are great for socialization, while individual walks offer more personalized attention. You can choose the option that best suits your dog's personality and requirements.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What safety measures do you have in place?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our dog walkers are fully insured, bonded, and trained in pet first aid. We use secure leashes and harnesses, avoid extreme weather conditions, and always carry water and waste bags. Additionally, we provide real-time updates and GPS tracking during walks for your peace of mind.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How do I schedule a dog walking service?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Scheduling is easy! Simply create an account on our app or website, input your dog's information and walking preferences, and choose your desired dates and times. You can book one-time walks or set up a recurring schedule for regular service.
